The paper presents an algorithm for feature selection in Big Data settings, which is a common problem in machine learning and data science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of statistical tests and meta-analysis techniques suggests a possible fit with cs.DM (Data Mining) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
